# Cursor Rules — Mohalla Project
# See AGENTS.md for full details.

# Project: Mohalla — Hyperlocal Vendor Digitalisation Platform
# Stack: React Native (Expo) · Next.js · Express · PostgreSQL · Claude API · Whisper API

# OWNERSHIP RULES:
# - backend/ and ai-services/ → Member A only
# - apps/vendor/ and apps/customer-pwa/ → Member B only
# - packages/shared-types/ → Both (with coordination)
# - NEVER modify files outside your ownership zone

# GIT RULES:
# - Always work on feature branches (feat/<owner>/<desc> or fix/<owner>/<desc>)
# - Use Conventional Commits
# - Never push directly to main

# CODE STYLE:
# - TypeScript strict mode
# - Named exports over default exports
# - camelCase for variables, PascalCase for types/components
# - Always handle errors explicitly
